{"tid":767120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界末日] 有冇巴打試過扁桃腺發炎","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T01:51:10.000Z","uid":133740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e95a69794558b85d1b92c8737ef72ceaad6c80","tid":767120,"uid":133740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"四日前扁桃腺發炎,返返吓工發高燒。<br />\n已經睇第三次醫生,兩邊扁桃腺勁多膿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛到乜都唔想做乜都唔想講,吞口水都要係心入面俾啲鼓勵自己先吞到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗食藥有冇方法食啲咩/飲啲咩會舒服啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce8cc64974c66fde7e09ca5f990d532ace3d1a7","tid":767120,"uid":17251,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"吞口水都痛果下先慘"},{"pid":"0c5995021bb6d61237c7e7a31981953c2c0a47f3","tid":767120,"uid":121909,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"飲涼茶or凍水 會舒服啲啲"},{"pid":"b11026d69a68b8e79747ddab75d7cc64d077c149","tid":767120,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"轉睇第個醫生 我個陣抖左一個禮拜到就好翻晒"},{"pid":"1aa69c5d4ba03380299b89e5e8ed5101f2e045dc","tid":767120,"uid":132382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e6315b4f10f5bd8e0649fe033c9c868e743bbc4","tid":767120,"uid":132106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n睇左兩次醫生 兩次都有抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2871681e5d918430a100d3605986326b901f17","tid":767120,"uid":133740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5995021bb6d61237c7e7a31981953c2c0a47f3","tid":767120,"uid":121909,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"飲涼茶or凍水 會舒服啲啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:20:3